<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirm Your Account</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100dvh;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: justify;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .logo img {
            max-width: 12rem;
            margin-left: -20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555555;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FC8C66 -4.17%, #F76A7B 110.42%);
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #333333;
        }

        .note {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .note a {
            color: transparent;
            text-decoration: none;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FC8C66 -4.17%, #F76A7B 110.42%);
            background-clip: text;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .note a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <!-- Insert logo here if needed -->
            <img height="57px" width="174x"  src="<%= logo %>" alt="myTamilDate Logo" />
        </div>
        <h1>Confirm your account</h1>
        <p>Please click the button below to confirm your email address and finish setting up your account. This link is
            valid for 48 hours.</p>
        <a href="<%= link %>" class="button">Confirm</a>
        <p class="note">If you didn't register in <a href="https://mytamildate.com/">mytamildate.com</a>. Please ignore this mail.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>